data.description: Exceptional 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 1 car garage home that has been loved and cared for, by a single owner, since it was built.  As you approach the home, instantly the charming curb appeal will grab your attention with lush landscape, manicured lawn, large covered front porch, tumbled brick wraps the entire home and includes a large, oversized east facing driveway. The main floor features a spacious family room, recessed lighting, open staircase, dedicated dining space, huge kitchen with tons of counter and cabinet space, 3 large bedrooms and an updated full bathroom. The main floor also has tons of natural light with huge newer windows throughout the main floor as well as hardwood floors under most of the carpet! The fully finished basement presents so many options! The family/rec room is ideal for a theater or gaming room! A full bar with countertop seating and an additional flex space that can be used for an office, pool table or could very easily convert to a 4th bedroom (closets and windows are already in place). The basement also features a bathroom with shower, several windows for natural light, tons of storage, cork walls (for sound proofing) and a dedicated laundry space (washer and dryer included). The large backyard is a private oasis with large mature trees, massive brick patio that is partially covered, a secondary entertaining space that has an included gazebo and storage shed that can be a shop! This home also has a brand-new roof installed in October 2023, newer furnace and AC unit, insulated garage door. This home is in great condition, light lived in and is an exceptional value with price per square foot!
